source:
TEXT_BANOMI124_04630_SEQ_00<tab>Stigma-4 requires the assistance of a life-form quick on their feet.

※Please note that the difficulty of this quest has been synced to your current level. Furthermore, you may not proceed with a class or job that is different from when you accepted this quest.
target:
TEXT_BANOMI124_04630_SEQ_00<tab><var 48 F201FC /var><var 49 F201FD /var>特殊ルール： レベルアジャスト受注クラス・ジョブ制限<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var>
※本クエストは受注時のクラスでのみ進行します。

リサーチA4のスティグマ・フォーは、素材調達を頼みたいようだ。

source: TEXT_BANOMI124_04630_SEQ_01<tab>Speak with the advanced culinary research unit at the Elysian playgrounds.
target: TEXT_BANOMI124_04630_SEQ_01<tab>エリュシオンの遊園区画で調理研究型オミクロンと話す

source: TEXT_BANOMI124_04630_SEQ_02<tab>Deliver the requested items to the advanced culinary research unit.
target: TEXT_BANOMI124_04630_SEQ_02<tab>調理研究型オミクロンに依頼された品を納品
TEXT_BANOMI124_04630_SEQ_03<tab>スティグマ・フォーに報告

TEXT_BANOMI124_04630_TODO_02<tab>スティグマ・フォーに報告

source: TEXT_BANOMI124_04630_STIGMA4_000_000<tab>Research is underway to develop a new menu for draconic patrons of the Last Dregs. At present, preliminary trials using resources available on Elysion are being performed to recreate the “taste of home” the dragons once enjoyed on their planet.
target:
TEXT_BANOMI124_04630_STIGMA4_000_000<tab>カフェの顧客となったドラゴン族のため、新メニューを研究中。
加えて、エリュシオンで採れる食材を使って、
彼らが故郷で捕食していた生物の味の再現を試みている。

source: TEXT_BANOMI124_04630_STIGMA4_000_001<tab>It has been proposed that an organic life-form's touch may aid in this effort, and for that reason, your services are requested. Receive the full mission briefing from the advanced culinary research unit stationed in the Elysion area dedicated to youth recreation.
target:
TEXT_BANOMI124_04630_STIGMA4_000_001<tab>同盟者<var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>にも協力を求む。
エリュシオン遊園区画で調理研究型オミクロンと合流し、
詳細内容を確認のうえ、任務を遂行せよ。

source: TEXT_BANOMI124_04630_DELIVERER04630_000_010<tab><whirr> Allied life-form recognized. This unit will now proceed to mission briefing.
target:
TEXT_BANOMI124_04630_DELIVERER04630_000_010<tab>ガガガ……同盟者<var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>と確認……
ドラゴン族が好む味の再現に関する任務ですね？
お待ちしておりました。

source: TEXT_BANOMI124_04630_DELIVERER04630_000_011<tab>Your mission is thus: procure samples of worms that appeal to the gustatory inputs of organic life-forms from rocky outcrops in the vicinity, and deliver them to present coordinates at maximum achievable speed.
target:
TEXT_BANOMI124_04630_DELIVERER04630_000_011<tab>遊園区画で「<var 28 ((Item)) F2959801 /var>」の採集を。
入手後は、速やかに納品を願います。

source: TEXT_BANOMI124_04630_DELIVERER04630_000_012<tab>Your mission is thus: procure samples of true dragon fruit from vegetation patches in the vicinity, and deliver them to present coordinates at maximum achievable speed.
target:
TEXT_BANOMI124_04630_DELIVERER04630_000_012<tab>遊園区画で「<var 28 ((Item)) F295B001 /var>」の採集を。
入手後は、速やかに納品を願います。

source: TEXT_BANOMI124_04630_DELIVERER04630_000_013<tab>Your mission is thus: procure a sample of dragon's delight from a water hole in the vicinity, and deliver it to present coordinates at maximum achievable speed. Use of gold salmon roe in its retrieval recommended.
target:
TEXT_BANOMI124_04630_DELIVERER04630_000_013<tab>遊園区画で「<var 28 ((Item)) F295C801 /var>」の採集を。
入手後は、速やかに納品を願います。
入手には<var 28 ((Item)) F28EEC01 /var>の使用が効果的です。

source: TEXT_BANOMI124_04630_DELIVERER04630_000_014<tab>Procure samples of worms that appeal to the gustatory inputs of organic life-forms from rocky outcrops in the vicinity, and deliver them to present coordinates at maximum achievable speed.
target:
TEXT_BANOMI124_04630_DELIVERER04630_000_014<tab>遊園区画で「<var 28 ((Item)) F2959801 /var>」の採集を。
入手後は、速やかに納品を願います。

source: TEXT_BANOMI124_04630_DELIVERER04630_000_015<tab>Procure samples of true dragon fruit from vegetation patches in the vicinity, and deliver them to present coordinates at maximum achievable speed.
target:
TEXT_BANOMI124_04630_DELIVERER04630_000_015<tab>遊園区画で「<var 28 ((Item)) F295B001 /var>」の採集を。
入手後は、速やかに納品を願います。

source: TEXT_BANOMI124_04630_DELIVERER04630_000_016<tab>Procure a sample of dragon's delight from a water hole in the vicinity, and deliver it to present coordinates at maximum achievable speed. Use of gold salmon roe in its retrieval recommended.
target:
TEXT_BANOMI124_04630_DELIVERER04630_000_016<tab>遊園区画で「<var 28 ((Item)) F295C801 /var>」の採集を。
入手後は、速やかに納品を願います。
入手には<var 28 ((Item)) F28EEC01 /var>の使用が効果的です。

source: TEXT_BANOMI124_04630_DELIVERER04630_000_020<tab><whirr> Analysis of allied life-form's dimpled facial expression suggests mission was successful. Immediate transfer of the requested items is desired.
target: TEXT_BANOMI124_04630_DELIVERER04630_000_020<tab>ガガガ……依頼品は入手できたでしょうか？

source: TEXT_BANOMI124_04630_DELIVERER04630_000_021<tab>Bzzzt... This unit can confirm the delivered items fall within acceptable parameters. Preparing to display appreciation for allied life-form's cooperation: thank you. Return to Stigma-4 for mission debriefing and compensation.
target:
TEXT_BANOMI124_04630_DELIVERER04630_000_021<tab>ガガガ……依頼品を確認……
この度の協力に感謝します。
「スティグマ・フォー」から報酬を、お受け取りください。

source: TEXT_BANOMI124_04630_STIGMA4_000_030<tab>The advanced culinary research unit sent communication of mission success. <var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>'s contribution was noted favorably.
target:
TEXT_BANOMI124_04630_STIGMA4_000_030<tab>調理研究型オミクロンより、報告を受信済み。
同盟者<var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>の協力を評価する。

source: TEXT_BANOMI124_04630_STIGMA4_000_031<tab>Current evaluation of the difficulty of mission to recreate comestibles native to the Dragonstar remains high at present, but within realistic boundaries nonetheless. Further analysis of available culinary methods necessary.
target:
TEXT_BANOMI124_04630_STIGMA4_000_031<tab>竜星由来の食材確保は難しいが、
調理することで、味や食感を近づけることは可能と推測。
現在、最適な調理法を研究中である。

source: TEXT_BANOMI124_04630_STIGMA4_000_032<tab>Additional problems are anticipated. The dragons' prodigious size necessitates that a sustainable means of amassing enough provisions to satisfy their appetite be determined. Research and development of aquaculture done in parallel may prove a promising solution...
target:
TEXT_BANOMI124_04630_STIGMA4_000_032<tab>ただし、調理法が確立されても、問題が残る。
巨体を誇るドラゴン族の腹を満たすには、相当量の食材が必須。
養殖技術の研究も、平行して行うべきと判断する……。
